title: Ekiben
creator: Sean Murphy
description: At most large train stations, you can buy an ekiben - a box lunch to be eaten on a shinkansen train. This was Sean's ekiben for our first shinkansen ride from Tokyo to Toyama. It was rice and beef, and it had a chemical heating feature where you would initiate the exothermal reaction that heated your food by pulling a string.
